    ÛÛÛÛÛÛ Using the Playlist ÛÛÛÛÛÛ
    ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ

    Vanadium Module Player a playlist which has got 32 slots.
    Each slot can be loaded with a module. You can get to
    the playlist from almost anywhere (except from dos-shell)
    by pressing F9.

    Following keys can be used in playlist:

    UP          goes one slot up
    DOWN        goes one slot down
    ENTER or    Goes to file selector. If file is selected
    INSERT          there it is placed into this slot
    DELETE      Deletes a song from memory (not from disk)
    SPACE       Plays this song
    ALT + N     Plays next song in the list
    ALT + P     Plays previous song in the list



